{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "text": "今天的天气很舒服，阳光透过窗帘落在桌面上。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/002.wav", "text": "请把手机调成静音，我们现在开始录音测试。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/003.wav", "text": "我喜欢在清晨散步，听树叶被风吹动的声音。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/004.wav", "text": "如果你准备好了，请连续读完这段完整的句子。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/005.wav", "text": "这杯咖啡有一点苦，不过香气非常浓郁。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/006.wav", "text": "昨天下午三点半，我在地铁二号线换乘到机场线。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/007.wav", "text": "会议预计持续四十五分钟，请提前五分钟入场。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/008.wav", "text": "现在是二零二六年三月二十二日，星期日。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/009.wav", "text": "这个项目的目标很明确：稳定、清晰、可维护。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/010.wav", "text": "你可以把音量降低到百分之三十，再试一次。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/011.wav", "text": "北方的冬天干燥寒冷，南方的夏天潮湿闷热。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/012.wav", "text": "我们已经完成第一阶段，接下来进入联调验证。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/013.wav", "text": "请确认文件名、采样率和保存路径都没有写错。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/014.wav", "text": "新版本修复了闪退问题，也优化了启动速度。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/015.wav", "text": "今天晚餐想吃清淡一点，比如番茄鸡蛋面。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/016.wav", "text": "这条路白天车很多，晚上反而安静不少。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/017.wav", "text": "我刚刚收到通知，系统将在零点进行升级维护。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/018.wav", "text": "他说话节奏很稳，语气平和，几乎没有停顿。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/019.wav", "text": "如果网络不稳定，上传过程可能会自动重试。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/020.wav", "text": "这个功能默认开启，也可以在设置里手动关闭。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/021.wav", "text": "轻舟已过万重山，回头看时只剩薄雾和远灯。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/022.wav", "text": "纸上得来终觉浅，绝知此事要躬行。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/023.wav", "text": "春风又绿江南岸，明月何时照我还。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/024.wav", "text": "小王去上海出差，小李在杭州参加培训。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/025.wav", "text": "请在十秒内读完这句，再自然停顿两秒。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/026.wav", "text": "我们需要一份更详细的报告，包含时间和结论。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/027.wav", "text": "数据显示，过去七天的请求成功率是百分之九十九点九。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/028.wav", "text": "今天先到这里，剩下的问题明天上午继续讨论。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/029.wav", "text": "她问我：你真的准备好了吗？我回答：当然。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/030.wav", "text": "这是一段中英文混读测试：OpenAI、MLX、Rust、API。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/031.wav", "text": "请读取这个版本号：v2.3.7-beta，注意连字符和小数点。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/032.wav", "text": "订单编号是 A9K7-4M2Q-88，收货地址稍后短信发送。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/033.wav", "text": "红鲤鱼与绿鲤鱼与驴，这句绕口令请自然朗读。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/034.wav", "text": "我们把复杂的问题拆成小步骤，就更容易解决。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
{"audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/035.wav", "text": "如果出现异常，请先截图，再记录复现步骤。", "ref_audio": "/Users/alan0x/Documents/projects/moxin-tts/scripts/finetune_speaker/yangyang_new/raw/001.wav", "language": "Chinese"}
